<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <title>Power of Attorney</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        padding: 40px;
        color: #000;
      }
      h1 {
        text-align: center;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .section {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>POWER OF ATTORNEY</h1>

    <div class='section'>
      {{city}},
      {{date}}, two thousand and twenty-five
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      I,
      {{fullName}}, born on
      {{birthDate}}, Taxpayer Identification Number
      {{tin}}, registered at the address:
      {{address}}, Passport
      {{passport}}, issued on
      {{passportIssueDate}}; understanding the meaning of my actions and acting voluntarily, on the basis of a prior
      mutual agreement, hereby I authorize
      {{representativeName}}, born on
      {{representativeBirthDate}}, Taxpayer Identification Number
      {{representativeTIN}}, registered at the address:
      {{representativeAddress}},
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      TO BE MY REPRESENTATIVE AND REPRESENT MY INTEREST before third parties in all relevant enterprises, institutions
      and organizations, regardless of their subordination, including state authorities, management and local
      self-government bodies, district administration, its departments, privatization bodies of Lviv City Council, in
      the city agency for housing privatization, Municipal Enterprise “City Agency for Housing Privatization”, Municipal
      Services Department of Lviv City Council, executive bodies of Lviv City Council, in notary offices, Municipal
      Enterprise “PRAVO”, Municipal Enterprise “Bureau of Technical Inventory” of Lviv City Council, State Registration
      Service of Ukraine (Ukrderzhregistr) and its structural subdivisions, Department of State Registration of Real
      Rights to Immovable Property of Lviv City Department of Justice, in associations of housing and communal services,
      Inspectorate of Architectural and Building Control in Lviv Region and its structural subdivisions, departments of
      architecture and construction, fire safety authorities, sanitary-epidemiological station, address bureau,
      Administrative Service Centers, expert appraisal organizations, with all the necessary powers in resolving any
      issues related to the privatization and registration of ownership in my name of the apartment located at the
      address:
      {{propertyAddress}}, receiving necessary documents, duplicate of documents, as well as with further DISPOSAL
      (sale, exchange, rent) of the above-mentioned property, on terms and at a price at her own discretion, with the
      right to conclude and sign on my behalf on terms at her own discretion purchase and sale agreement, rental
      agreement, exchange agreement, preliminary agreement, agreement on amendments and/or additions to the above
      agreements, agreements on termination of the above agreements, etc.
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      For this purpose, I do hereby authorize her to submit and receive on my behalf the necessary certificates,
      documents, statements, technical documents, reports, extracts, copies, etc., permits, registration and title
      documents, incl. documents on ownership of real estate, certificates, Extract / Information from the State
      Register of Real Rights to Immovable Property on the registration of ownership; to submit statements on my behalf
      to relevant authorities and institutions, including statements for the issuance of duplicate documents, statements
      for state registration of rights and their encumbrances, statements for my marital status and/or ownership of
      property by personal private property right, statements for error correction; to receive the necessary
      certificates and documents, including title documents, duplicates of title documents, any documents, including
      Certificate of ownership of real estate (or its duplicate), Information certificates and/or Extracts from the
      State Register of Real Rights to Immovable Property; to sign for me on documents and their receipt, conclude and
      sign on my behalf preliminary agreements, purchase and sale agreements, agreement on amendments and/or additions
      to the above agreements, rental agreements, agreements on termination of the above agreements, etc.; to open and
      close accounts in my name in any banking institutions, carry out non-cash settlements, receive funds due to me,
      pay the cost of services for processing documents, administrative fees, state duty, taxes and other necessary
      payments, as well as perform all other actions related to this Power of Attorney.
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      The Power of Attorney is issued with the right of substitution for a period of THREE YEARS and is valid until
      {{validUntil}}.
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      Signature: ____________________
      {{fullName}}
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

